MARK RIETMEIJER (SCULPTOR)
Mark Rietmeijer, sculptor and friend. Three weeks ago a new block of marble arrived in his studio. I decided to make pictures of the creation of his new work of art.
So from now on I'll upload pictures on a regular base, showing the process of creation. 
